Working in the yard
The family is working on the yard.
The mother is wearing a magenta blouse and hat.
The father is wearing a shirt, shorts and gloves.
The son is wearing a purple shirt with tan shorts.
Mowing the lawn
The boy is mowing the lawn near the white fence.
He is pushing a green lawn mower.
Bringing new flowers
The father is carrying a box of plants.
He is bringing plants to the mother.
Planting new flowers
The mother is sitting next to the planting bed.
She is planting new flowers.
The flowers are yellow and white.
